TextEng: Could I trouble you with some questions?
Me wants to ask questions from you.
Goodbye.
Me want to know about different city areas.
Text: 나 도시 다른 구역들 알고 싶어.

TextEng: Can you tell me anything about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭐라도 말해줄 수 있나요?

TextEng: I require some information about locations in Neverwinter.
Is there anything odd that you have heard?
You knows much about the plague?
Me wants to have information about Neverwinter places.
Maybe yous heard some rumors or something?
What do you know about cure attempts?
Text: 치료제를 찾으려는 시도에 대해 뭘 알아요?

TextEng: You know about cure attempts maybe?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Has the plague disrupted the social order of the city?
I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Are you suggesting a revolt of some sort?
What are the different areas of the city?
Tell me about the Beggar's Nest.
Tell me about the Docks district.
Tell me about the Blacklake district.
Tell me about the Peninsula.
Where can I get equipment?
Where me get equipment?
Tell me about the City Core.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Certainly you can tell me.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You can tell me. Why worries about me?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 너 말해 줄 수 있어. 왜 나 걱정해?

TextEng: Certainly you can tell me? We are <race> kin.
Text: 분명 말해주실 수 있겠죠? 우린 같은 <race> 혈족이에요.

TextEng: We both <race> kind. Why not tell me?
Text: 우리 둘 다 <race>야. 왜 말 안 해?

TextEng: You tells about City Core.
You tells about Beggar's Nest.
You tells about the Docks district.
You tells about the Blacklake.
You tells about Peninsula.
I need to ask about other city districts.
Me ask about other areas?
You look very wealthy. Are you?
You look like a rich lady. You rich, lady?
Text: 너 부자처럼 보여. 너 부자야, 아가씨?

TextEng: Give me gold or I'll drag you through the Beggar's Nest.
Text: 금을 주세요, 안 그러면 거지 소굴로 끌고 갈 거예요.

TextEng: You gives gold or me pull yous through Beggar's Nest!
Text: 너 금 내, 안 그러면 나 너 거지 소굴로 끌고 갈 거야!

TextEng: Merely curious. Let's go back to my other questions.
Text: 그냥 궁금했을 뿐이에요. 다른 질문으로 돌아가죠.

TextEng: Me just interested. Back to other questions now, okay?
Text: 나 그냥 궁금했어. 이제 다른 질문 할게, 알았지?

TextEng: I'm a guard. I can do what I want. I'll pull you through the dirty, filthy Beggar's Nest!
Text: 전 경비병이에요. 제 맘대로 할 수 있죠. 더럽고 냄새나는 거지 소굴로 끌고 갈 거예요!

TextEng: Me guard. Me do what me want. Me haul you through stinky, dirty Beggar's Nest!
Text: 나 경비병이야. 나 내 맘대로 해. 나 너 더럽고 냄새나는 거지 소굴로 끌고 갈 거야!

TextEng: I beg your pardon, ma'am. I did not mean to say that.
Text: 죄송합니다, 부인. 그런 말을 하려던 게 아니에요.

TextEng: Me sorry. Me not mean to say stuff to yous.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 그런 말 하려던 거 아니었어.
